    "description": "Vision Express India Asia Pacific Associates, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Marketplace Manager for our Thane operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout Vision Express India Asia Pacific Associates:\nVision Express India Asia Pacific Associates is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Coordinate with vendors and suppliers for inventory management\n• Conduct competitor analysis and market benchmarking\n• Manage customer reviews, ratings, and return/refund processes\n• Manage marketplace relationships with Amazon, Flipkart, and Meesho\n• Develop and implement category growth strategies\n• Create engaging content for product pages and social media\n• Manage email marketing campaigns and push notifications\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBBS / MD / MS from recognized medical college\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Customer Segmentation\n• Proficiency in Facebook Ads\n• Proficiency in Product Management\n• Proficiency in Affiliate Marketing\n• Proficiency in Google Analytics\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in Digital Marketing\n• Proficiency in Email Marketing\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Thane, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Vision Express India Asia Pacific Associates!",
